sublet.translation[0].definitions[0].def: to rent to someone else a property that you rent from its owner
sublet.translation[0].definitions[0].exa: I sublet my apartment to my sister, packed my van, and headed west.
sublet.translation[1].definitions[0].def: to rent property that you rent from its owner to another person
